    "rich_text_CYhByq": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_QDPdjB": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Super Kid Mohair",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_bBVMFx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Super kid mohair comes from a single moment in an Angora goat’s life — the first and only shearing that produces fibre this fine. The yield is small, which is why it costs more, and why it feels entirely different from ordinary mohair. It’s lighter, softer, and far more refined, giving warmth without weight and a texture that stays clean and controlled. We use it for one reason: when a piece relies on comfort, precision, and a clearly higher level of quality, nothing else performs the same. A rare material, chosen for the moments when the difference is meant to be felt.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
