    "rich_text_AEL7Nq": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_VJVyGr": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why Only 99 Pieces",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_YybAYE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Limiting each collection to 99 pieces is a choice, not a gimmick. Producing in small numbers allows us to focus on quality at a level that isn’t possible with volume — no shortcuts, no overstock, no pieces waiting to be discounted. What we make is exactly what we stand behind, and the price you see is the price it will always be. When you find your number on the label, you’re holding one of only 99 pieces created with that intention.</p>"
          }
        }
